title: SMW Central Hacks Extreme
description:
The package contains many SMW hacks

The package includes demo version, full version and kaizo.

System requirements:

Intel Core 2 Duo E8400 @ 3 GHz or AMD Phenom X4 945 3 GHz

1 GB RAM

Video card with video memory up to 256 MB

(NVIDIA GeForce 7600 GT or AMD Radeon HD 3470)

7.9 GB free space

Mouse and Keyboard are required

High-definition Audio needed

Joystick (optional)

OS Supported: Windows Vista SP2,

Windows 7 SP1, Windows 8.1 Update 3

and Windows 10
